&lt;p&gt;Bank Staff Nurse - Inpatient Unit&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;£14.75 per hour, plus relevant shift enhancements&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Relief/Bank&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Location: Bray, Maidenhead&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Thames Hospice, we are always interested in meeting nurses who would like to come and work for us on a relief/casual basis for our 17 bed Inpatient Unit delivering skilled and compassionate care to our patients and their families.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will have experience as a registered nurse – not necessarily in a hospice or palliative care setting – with the desire to care for this group of patients. You should possess good communication skills, excellent care values and a strong sense of team spirit.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Visit our website and watch our video to find out what it&#39;s like being a nurse at Thames Hospice.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For an informal discussion about the role, please contact Sarah Johnston, Head of Clinical Services on &lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;sarah.johnston@thameshospice.org.uk &lt;/span&gt;or 01753 848925..&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This appointment is subject to an Enhanced Disclosure and Barring Service check, including barred lists.&lt;/p&gt;
